      <h4>AWS SysOps Engineer – Valenture Institute | Jan 2025 – Present</h4>

      <p><b>Company:</b> Ed-tech provider delivering accredited online education including UCT Online High School.</p>

      <p><b>Responsibilities:</b></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Manage and optimise multi-environment AWS cloud infrastructure ensuring high availability, performance, and security</li>
