      <h4>IT Business Analyst – Excellerate Property Services | May 2012 – May 2022</h4>

      <p><b>Responsibilities:</b></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Tier 1–3 support for NICOR, SAP, MDA systems</li>
        <li>User onboarding, offboarding, and access management</li>
